        = \lim_{h\to0} \frac{4t^{2}+8th+4h^{2}+4-4t^{2}-4}{h}
        = \lim_{h\to0} 8t+4h = 8 t
and
v(t) = \lim_{h\to0} \frac{8\mathopen{}\left(t+h\right) - 8t}{h}
        = \lim_{h\to0} \frac{8t+8h-8t}{h}
        = \lim_{h\to0} 8 = 8.

